text: Sonali is a popular Indian or Southeast Asian female given name. == Persons == * Sonali Bendre, a Bollywood actress * Sonali Chowdhury, Bengali actress * Sonali Kulkarni, a Bollywood actress * Sonali Gulati, a US-based filmmaker * Sonali Shah, a UK TV presenter and newsreader == See also == * Sonal Category:Indian feminine given names
